232
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:30,400
Eh?

233
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:31,400
Hm?

234
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:35,640
Je Ranko ten typ dieťaťa, čo zanedbáva svojho bratranca?

235
00:14:37,470 --> 00:14:39,140
Chápem.

236
00:14:41,430 --> 00:14:42,560
Je to tu.

237
00:14:42,560 --> 00:14:44,270
Viem.

238
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,410
Chihiro-kun.

239
00:14:57,310 --> 00:14:59,150
Hej, hej, Chihiro-kun.

240
00:14:59,150 --> 00:14:59,870
Čo?

241
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,850
Prečo si nezoberieme nejaké anime?

242
00:15:01,850 --> 00:15:04,220
Majú tu zopár zaujímavých.

243
00:15:04,220 --> 00:15:06,050
Toto je zaujímavé.

244
00:15:13,520 --> 00:15:16,370
Zombie akadémia: Tragédia na kultúrnom festivale.

245
00:15:16,370 --> 00:15:19,310
Ah, ako sa dalo od Chihiro-kuna čakať.

246
00:15:19,310 --> 00:15:20,300
V tom prípade,

247
00:15:20,300 --> 00:15:24,310
