305
00:18:58,380 --> 00:19:00,760
Tak poďme do tých zvyšných dvoch domov.

306
00:19:02,050 --> 00:19:02,700
Chihiro.

307
00:19:02,700 --> 00:19:04,030
Hm?

308
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:09,120
Držme sa za ruky.

309
00:19:09,120 --> 00:19:10,790
Prečo?

310
00:19:11,830 --> 00:19:13,600
Nepýtaj sa. Len ma drž za ruku.

311
00:19:13,600 --> 00:19:14,410
