335
00:20:29,630 --> 00:20:31,560
Máme tam dosť rúk.

336
00:20:31,560 --> 00:20:32,700
Naozaj?!

337
00:20:32,700 --> 00:20:34,830
Mám šťastie!

338
00:20:34,830 --> 00:20:36,710
Maj sa.

339
00:20:46,040 --> 00:20:46,850
Čo je?

340
00:20:50,010 --> 00:20:50,700
Čo...

341
00:20:50,700 --> 00:20:52,350
